premise_source_doc_sentence: Yeon Sang-ho  (  born 1978  )  is a South Korean film director and screenwriter .
He wrote and directed the animated films The King of Pigs  (  2011  )  and The Fake  (  2013  )  , and the live-action film Train to Busan  (  2016  )  .
The Fake is a 2013 South Korean animated film written and directed by Yeon Sang-ho .
Train to Busan is a 2016 South Korean zombie apocalypse action thriller film directed by Yeon Sang-ho and starring Gong Yoo , Jung Yu-mi , and Ma Dong-seok .
Psychokinesis is an upcoming South Korean black comedy film directed by Yeon Sang-ho .
Yeon Sang-ho  (  born 1978  )  is a South Korean film director and screenwriter .
He wrote and directed the animated films The King of Pigs  (  2011  )  and The Fake  (  2013  )  , and the live-action film Train to Busan  (  2016  )  .
